      <Value><![CDATA[Physiotherapy Science, University of Bergen, Bergen, Norway]]></Value>
    </articleReference>
    <articleTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[A randomised, placebo controlled trial of low level laser therapy for activated Achilles tendinitis with microdialysis measurement of peritendinous prostaglandin E2 concentrations]]></Value>
    </articleTitle>
